task.summary: -Utils-Library updated. -Workspace and project preferences updated for newest Android Studio
-Flash from file browser on some devices fixed
-Better unified builds handling -Style fixes (cards now dark to)
-Now normal reboot after kernel flashing instead of recovery reboot
-Turkish translations fixed and updated by Fathi Firinci
-Backup Manager now a own Fragment -Backup Manager is accesible over the menu in the Flash screen -Report Dialog now is a own class
-Cannot send report if comment is to big fixed

Update [2.2.8]
-Cannot send report if comment is to big fixed (thanks for reporting XDA-Member Stilez) -Update crashes fixed! -Better version formating for stock images -Chinese translation by XDA-Member dlhxr -UI changes
-Fixed backup and restore bug on ICS and lower (Please rename backups without using ':')
-Errors on setting new file permissions with toolbox (old devices doesn't include chmod in toolbox)
-Better click effect -Title and content separator removed

Update [2.2.9]
-Working back to 2.2 again! -Errors on setting new file permissions with toolbox (old devices doesn't include chmod in toolbox) -New icon (with lennoardrai@****.com) -Some UI changes -New colors -Startup update crash fixed -Fixed backup and restore bug on ICS and lower (Please rename backups without using ':')
